<center><textEffects>22nd November, 9:00 a.m.
Supreme Court of Judicature, Courtroom 2</textEffects></center>
<line>
Ryunosuke:
So this... is a courtroom... 
</line><line>Kazuma:
<textEffects>The Supreme Court of Judicature</textEffects>. No court in the land has more power. 
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
