Forgive me for intruding on court proceedings, Your Excellency.
</line><line>Susato:
<textEffects>Susato Mikotoba</textEffects>, judicial assistant to the defence.
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
<textEffects>(<span style="color:#E16935">Mikotoba</textEffects>...? In my darkest hour, with nowhere left to go, she appeared like a bolt of lightning. And in her hand...she carried a small <textEffects>package</textEffects>, wrapped in a furoshiki cloth...)</span>
