</line><line>Ryunosuke:
Yes, Your Excellency.
</line><line>Kazuma:
I remember him saying that he was up to something with his koban coin when it happened. At exactly the moment the gun was fired.
</line>
<hr />
<line>Korekuta:
The gunshot interested me not. I was far too busy on the floor.
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
