</line><line>Nosa:
</line>
<center>.........
......U......</center>
<line>UWAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAClippety-clop, clippety-clop, clippety-clop, clippety-clop, clippety-clop, clippety-clop!GAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAGH!!!Nippon Imperial Army, Sergeant Iyesa Nosa, preparing to stand down in the Supreme Court, sir!
