</line><line>Auchi:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/e/e2/Objection_Ryu_English.png/revision/latest?cb=20210426093406" class="image"><img alt="Objection Ryu English" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="187" data-image-name="Objection Ryu English.png" data-image-key="Objection_Ryu_English.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/e/e2/Objection_Ryu_English.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20210426093406" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Auchi:
But... What is your actual point? Perhaps the delightful Miss Brett was ravenously hungry and couldn't help her-
</line><line>Brett:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/4/44/Shutup%21.png/revision/latest?cb=20220420195556" class="image"><img alt="Shutup!" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="184" data-image-name="Shutup!.png" data-image-key="Shutup%21.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/4/44/Shutup%21.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20220420195556" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Brett:
.........
</line><line>Auchi:
Oh, um... Whatever you say, dear lady!
</line><line>Brett:
As I said, I really must be leaving now. Afternoon tea with the Minister of Justice cannot possibly wait any longer.
</line><line>Auchi:
Of course, of course! This will all be over in the blink of an eye! Rest assured, I'm about to put this rookie in his place! Just leave everything to-
</line><line>Brett:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/4/44/Shutup%21.png/revision/latest?cb=20220420195556" class="image"><img alt="Shutup!" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="184" data-image-name="Shutup!.png" data-image-key="Shutup%21.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/4/44/Shutup%21.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20220420195556" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Brett:
I've heard enough... You irritating little spectacled samurai relic!
</line><line>Auchi:
Of, of course...dear ladyyyyyyyy!
</line><line>Kazuma:
What's the matter, Miss Brett? Have we ruffled your feathers?
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
Clearly, the witness knows what this means. She's realised the catastrophic implications these <textEffects>teeth marks</textEffects> in the steak have for her!
</line><line>Kazuma:
Ryunosuke! Do you know where you're going with this?
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
<textEffects>(Yes. Now at last, it's all come together. The mysterious <span style="color:#E16935">teeth marks</textEffects> in a steak that had allegedly been eaten with cutlery... The reason why <textEffects>the bloodstain</textEffects> I know I saw somehow seems to have disappeared... And most importantly... <textEffects>The evidence</textEffects> that proves once and for all... who shot Dr Wilson that day!)</span>
</line><line>Judge:
I accept that these teeth marks in the steak are a little... 'unnatural', as you put it, Counsel. But what exactly are you suggesting that tells us?
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
...<textEffects>Everything</textEffects>, Your Excellency.
</line><line>Auchi:
Everything?!
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
Yes, I believe that these 'barbaric' teeth marks in the steak here... ...amount to conclusive evidence in this case. Evidence that will prove beyond any doubt who shot Dr Wilson!
</line><line>Brett:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/4/44/Shutup%21.png/revision/latest?cb=20220420195556" class="image"><img alt="Shutup!" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="184" data-image-name="Shutup!.png" data-image-key="Shutup%21.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/4/44/Shutup%21.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20220420195556" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Brett:
Conclusive evidence? How many times have I heard that today? You wouldn't know the meaning of the phrase! Typical Japanese empty threats!
</line><line>Kazuma:
How can you be so sure?
</line><line>Brett:
Oh, it's quite simple. If you really had such conclusive evidence, you would have presented it to the court long ago!
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
Actually, the evidence I'm talking about hasn't been brought before the court yet.
</line><line>Auchi:
Hasn't been...? What?!
</line><line>Ryunosuke:
But just because it hasn't been shown yet, doesn't mean that the evidence does not exist.
</line><line>Auchi:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/e/e2/Objection_Ryu_English.png/revision/latest?cb=20210426093406" class="image"><img alt="Objection Ryu English" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="187" data-image-name="Objection Ryu English.png" data-image-key="Objection_Ryu_English.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/e/e2/Objection_Ryu_English.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20210426093406" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Auchi:
